---

## Recommended Actions

### Digital/UX
1. **Add clear redemption preference settings in the rewards dashboard, allowing customers to easily switch between cashback and points.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~7 calls (1.4%)
2. **Display merchant category code (MCC) and applied earn rate for each transaction in the transaction history, with an explainer for category mapping.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~3 calls (0.6%)
3. **Implement an in-app offer tracker with a progress bar and a clear checklist of qualifying criteria for welcome bonuses.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~2 calls (0.4%)
4. **Implement proactive 60-day advance notifications (push, email, in-app) for upcoming tier downgrades, clearly outlining lost benefits.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~1 calls (0.2%)

### Operations

*No recommendations for Operations.*

### Communication
1. **Provide clear in-app guidance on redemption preferences during onboarding and ensure an easily accessible option to change them.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~7 calls (1.4%)
2. **Implement an in-app explainer for merchant category codes and their impact on bonus earnings. Display the applied earn rate per transaction in the transaction history.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~4 calls (0.8%)
3. **Provide clear communication on bonus fulfillment status, including reasons for partial fulfillment, and an in-app offer tracker with progress.** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~2 calls (0.4%)
4. **Send 60-day advance notifications for tier downgrades across multiple channels (push, email, in-app).** — Rewards & Loyalty — Reduces ~1 calls (0.2%)

### Policy

*No recommendations for Policy.*

